{"tid":511193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業漢虐殺15歲私影女 頭臉纏膠紙狂灌酒再侵犯","createTime":"2017-12-27T08:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T11:06:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"d9088bba80e6f5c477593a3ba793422a9630a443","tid":511193,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"中年無業漢相約年僅15歲私影模特兒到其旺角甘芳街的寓所拍照，期間疑因私影女拒絕依從其要求換衫而遭他虐殺。無業漢涉用茄汁樽狂扑對方頭部，再用膠紙將對方手及頭緊緊纏著在一起，又用尼龍繩綁住對方頸部。及後他見對方沒有反應，復用中式餐酒狂灌入對方喉嚨，然後脫下對方衣服大肆非禮，及暴力侵犯其私處。<br />\n<br />\n無業漢劉璋輝(34歲)否認於2014年12月8日謀殺15歲私影女郭惠明，案件今在高院開審，控方於開案陳詞中形容被告的行為「恐怖及令人嘔心」，並指被告向警方透露郭於寓所時已明顯沒有呼吸及心跳。<br />\n<br />\n法醫驗屍後證實郭乃窒息至死，而法醫指郭被膠紙完全封著口鼻和被人用尼龍繩綁頸，均會令她窒息至死。<br />\n<br />\n據控方透露，女死者郭惠明於中四綴學，她注重外表，與普通香港年青人無異，閒時會做兼職侍應賺取外快，亦曾擔任私影模特兒，她沒有固定男友。<br />\n<br />\n被告與郭由2014年12月初開始透過短訊聯絡，被告詢問郭是否私影模特兒，並查問對方身高體重。雙方最終同意於12月8日見面，郭同意收取500元拍照兩小時。郭曾要求先看私影當日的衣著，被告則稱會與她一同於朗豪坊購買服飾。<br />\n<br />\n而郭於被告寓所遇害後，遭被告塞進一個行李喼，被告然後清潔寓所，之後將行李喼拖到尖沙咀豪畔酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514362423_24b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514362423_24b4.jpg&h=dba8d2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者郭惠明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514362424_d069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514362424_d069.jpg&h=8b806658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告劉璋輝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632125&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=44fb1fed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632125&h=92149f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632125</a>"},{"pid":"e3b2a79c8865132452cc3c81361772d064035e1b","tid":511193,"uid":28195,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"風雨蘭成日提姊妹開工要小心安全，接少次客好過命都無埋"},{"pid":"67241b9d75345a659522f7c4711dc4daec728e31","tid":511193,"uid":53554,"like":17,"dislike":206,"score":-189,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac481a25122f5d0ea0e525c255cda5a1a55d8ec","tid":511193,"uid":84869,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"67241b9d75345a659522f7c4711dc4daec728e31","tid":511193,"uid":53554,"like":17,"dislike":206,"score":-189,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"死人你都硬？"},{"pid":"e95a1ab9404a857cccf160378873f045df23b116","tid":511193,"uid":55614,"like":129,"dislike":2,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 毒撚好恐怖"},{"pid":"ff62194ac95ba1ea0927d3cd7150742a7c877fd0","tid":511193,"uid":84869,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"e3b2a79c8865132452cc3c81361772d064035e1b","tid":511193,"uid":28195,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"風雨蘭成日提姊妹開工要小心安全，接少次客好過命都無埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"去人屋企<br />\n唔係自己地方開工就一定危險"},{"pid":"61c080a97baadcf842be11e9b2171923ed725fcc","tid":511193,"uid":38426,"like":11,"dislike":90,"score":-79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"唉 條女咁靚比我屌咪好囉<br />\n慘遭毒手 好可憐"},{"pid":"f9813a6a09194eb429251b9d9e0eb5897cc31af4","tid":511193,"uid":48579,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"她沒有固定男友 即係有流動男友？"},{"pid":"59373ba708fef09cda6a5afa46711c75a072c579","tid":511193,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"d360bfd05391591c082