壞腦，<br />\n好多人都鍾意睇sm 片包括我自己，但我係少少sm<br />\nSm av 男人鍾意睇應該係滿足大男人主義和絕對服從優越感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f3941462a4c8ed6bdb6294fd071a6a5bf520d8","tid":511193,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"好痴線<br />\n佢咁做完全唔怕會整死人？睇得暴力電影/av多 腦short short地<br />\n個女仔叫好地地搵錢 咁就冇命 <br />\n人渣"},{"pid":"5ef90dbc9cd2f607634877d54281ac38c1af32a9","tid":511193,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"哩啲要判終身<br />\n放返出黎分分鐘又多個受害者"},{"pid":"9b82143aedb92a153eda3c01524fc446b19288f2","tid":511193,"uid":23423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中年無業漢相約年僅15歲私影模特兒到其旺角甘芳街的寓所拍照，期間疑因私影女拒絕依從其要求換衫而遭他虐殺。無業漢涉用茄汁樽狂扑對方頭部，再用膠紙將對方手及頭緊緊纏著在一起，又用尼龍繩綁住對方頸部。及後他見對方沒有反應，復用中式餐酒狂灌入對方喉嚨，然後脫下對方衣服大肆非禮，及暴力侵犯其私處。<br />\n<br />\n無業漢劉璋輝(34歲)否認於2014年12月8日謀殺15歲私影女郭惠明，案件今在高院開審，控方於開案陳詞中形容被告的行為「恐怖及令人嘔心」，並指被告向警方透露郭於寓所時已明顯沒有呼吸及心跳。<br />\n<br />\n法醫驗屍後證實郭乃窒息至死，而法醫指郭被膠紙完全封著口鼻和被人用尼龍繩綁頸，均會令她窒息至死。<br />\n<br />\n據控方透露，女死者郭惠明於<span style=\"color: red;\">中四綴學</span>，她注重外表，與普通香港年青人無異，閒時會做兼職侍應賺取外快，亦曾擔任私影模特兒，她<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有固定男友</span>。<br />\n<br />\n被告與郭由2014年12月初開始透過短訊聯絡，被告詢問郭是否私影模特兒，並查問對方身高體重。雙方最終同意於12月8日見面，郭同意收取500元拍照兩小時。郭曾要求先看私影當日的衣著，被告則稱會與她一同於朗豪坊購買服飾。<br />\n<br />\n而郭於被告寓所遇害後，遭被告塞進一個行李喼，被告然後清潔寓所，之後將行李喼拖到尖沙咀豪畔酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514362423_24b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514362423_24b4.jpg&h=dba8d2b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者郭惠明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514362424_d069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514362424_d069.jpg&h=8b806658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告劉璋輝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632125&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=44fb1fed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632125&h=92149f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632125</a></blockquote><br />\n與普通香港年青人無異？<br />\n定淨係講注重外表一句?"},{"pid":"3766c4f4fba672bffb7dbe74b7c7fc55e436bdf5","tid":511193,"uid":47029,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"條仔似似地running man個gary"},{"pid":"7f2b5087e0920c674050ee392bb6133303815e5f","tid":511193,"uid":12755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"個樣毒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿拿聲拉佢打靶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8c53a094727042f8d03b5bd0cc716382054193","tid":511193,"uid":101485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509f1c1336f77faabc6df2a1025587d1aac7da2c","tid":511193,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"仲以為係d歐美國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f966e2a55916d21c914e0fc46730a9a9e5453e","tid":511193,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3ce6b39b0ab1d5bfd007cfacf1273c3c5a9bba","tid":511193,"uid":71624,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"肯撚定又減刑又盛，坐廿年走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d根本應該判終身<img src=\"/assets/fa